available.areacode: Code representing typically the largest sub-division in a country (e.g. State code).
available.areaname: Name relating to the AreaCode (e.g. State name).
available.countrycode: Country code (based on ISO3166 alpha-2 codes)
available.geogname1: Geography name: Descriptor of the geographical area.
available.geogscheme1: Geography scheme: Descriptor of the geography scheme used.
available.postalcode: Postcode: the highest resolution postcode most often used.
available.reinstag: User defined reinsurance tag to provide a further option for specifying reinsurance scope
